{"tid":675734,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全盛時期森巴足球飛機區","createTime":"2018-05-23T19:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T07:26:17.000Z","uid":66351,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"267866bf089a98ec64cd71d6de83b5e942da82be","tid":675734,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"不知不覺尼馬26歲，名義2億但實際表現如何大家心裡有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前幾日望住巴西份名單 除咗尼馬 只有保連奴依個靠好運補射同卡斯米路 不死式防中  加個古一招同耶蘇仔就話「先過咗兩三年唔夠就人才濟濟天才輩出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n唔係仲掛住馬些路同艾維斯掛（艾維斯好慘 應該最後一屆都冇得踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n當年 比利 黑珍珠唔使講 加隻小鳥 同鬍鬚仔 同埋渣仙奴 稱霸世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後 薛高 同蘇古迪斯 加埋 科高 同 白蘭高 無冠但贏盡所有人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再之後 靠住鄧加做防中 加埋羅馬里奧同白必圖 又再重現所謂森巴味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就係好多人耳熟能詳的大細哨加李華度 再夾卡富 卡路士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  尤其大哨依條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實佢唔係九十分鐘都係世界級表現  只係勤追波 而且一成功搶到波就會著曬火成為好得人驚的世界級球王表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟撚住入埋你 其餘時間都唔會在狀態 例如98 02決賽之類 阿叔佢地都話大哨冇咩態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但最後又有能力入到波 吹佢唔脹咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP祖同扭波王丹尼臣就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後已經係卡卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （咩柏圖呀 羅賓奴 法比安奴同阿祖安奴就算把啦）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇翻依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  失幾多入幾多的森巴味呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泰法路<br />\n卡富 盧斯奧 卡路士<br />\n鄧加<br />\n加連查 拖士圖 薛高 李維連奴<br />\n比利 朗拿度 <br />\n<br />\n後備： 細哨 羅馬里奧 李華度 白必圖 蘇古迪斯 白蘭高 渣仙奴<br />\n<br />\n有前冇後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打死罷就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩c朗美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3469592f1d331114b87cf02fe438a9f5c3bf606d","tid":675734,"uid":70415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"鍾意細哨，唔止佢啲球技，仲有佢踢波帶比人既快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881bdb45d6f9c915c121446f8aa244698a7092bd","tid":675734,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3469592f1d331114b87cf02fe438a9f5c3bf606d","tid":675734,"uid":70415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"鍾意細哨，唔止佢啲球技，仲有佢踢波帶比人既快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"望左傳右之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6384443462b3329fbf254c9df08f49fd21edee1","tid":675734,"uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"02年世盃<br />\n3R+卡富卡路士<br />\n而家點砌都無嗰種屈機既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae5b10076075159d5034d25c85e77db3c1f0063","tid":675734,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"樓主唔識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家隊巴西守力超強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570cdd40c333600cee376fec30a64f6628f3b16c","tid":675734,"uid":13090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"第一個偶像係李華度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1678e0cbfd88a40d656259692475b542686bc317","tid":675734,"uid":51250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n咩c朗美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98dd3b1f3a6d7a50bcba15c03102546bc86096f","tid":675734,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ae5b10076075159d5034d25c85e77db3c1f0063","tid":675734,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"樓主唔識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家隊巴西守力超強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"但係嗰種味道已經變晒<br />\n以前真係個個位都有個獨當一面嘅球員<br />\n唔係話而家差<br />\n但真係冇以前果種屈機嘅霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7ab01be61708b4c4b18c595732ad28223663c9","tid":675734,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"馬些路垃圾黎"},{"pid":"c99e95280097120cd86a083c93640fec0e89863b","tid":675734,"uid":66351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6384443462b3329fbf254c9df08f49fd21edee1","tid":675734,"uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"02年世盃<br />\n3R+卡富卡路士<br />\n而家點砌都無嗰種屈機既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"砌唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要遠射有遠射 要隊上去又有 要爆發要過人都有 邊似依家咁長傳同創造力好少少就吹到球王咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4deebebe83d20607e6b0e21b4c06719e0f3aee37","tid":675734,"uid":66351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ae5b10076075159d5034d25c85e77db3c1f0063","tid":675734,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"樓主唔識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家隊巴西守力超強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"到底邊個唔識呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個做中堅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16172bdba16f152a2fa0ed35a8283e69d07d147","tid